Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&H0001FF&\pos(957,1068)}向右向右轉啊轉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&H0001FF&\pos(957,1068)}仰視天空上午好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&H0001FF&\pos(957,1068)}朝向下面上午好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&H0001FF&\pos(957,1068)}握起拳頭嗨嗨嗨
